      • getID

        public java.lang.String getID()
        Description copied from class: LocalInspectionTool
        If you want to change suppression id you have to define it in XML as well.

        Inspection tool ID is a descriptive name to be used in "suppress" comments and annotations.

        It must satisfy LocalInspectionTool.VALID_ID_PATTERN regexp pattern.

        If not defined InspectionProfileEntry.getShortName() is used as tool ID.

        Overrides:
        getID in class LocalInspectionTool
        Returns:
        inspection tool ID.
